channel.title: Stupid computer re-boot just basic once again :p
channel.description:
Well i have just re imaged my whole comp and put windows and everything back on (i did do a back up of everything) But now the Classpath and PATH bit in the system is all together right but it comes up with.
[code]Error opening registry key 'Software\JavaSoft\Java Runtime Environment' Error: could not find java.dll Error: could not find Java 2 Runtime Environment. [/code]
I've never had that before in my whole about 3 months + of private servers. Even though i haven't even played private servers since November Earlier December so don't expect me to remember everything still.
Thanks in advance. If you help out you will get a mod place on my once good server.
